snippet.title: Strife: The Expanse Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1566500/Strife_The_Expanse/

Trailer of my new and upcoming game Strife: The Expanse. A hex grid turn based strategy game played on procedurally generated battlefields. Fight against your friends or AI in free for all or team battles!

Oculus VR is also supported!
